result.name: Ho Shing Restaurant

reviews.text: Very local , great egg puffle,  good checkered cake
Good. Easy. And nice staffs
Good breakfast but fair lunch food
Good HK style tea shop..

A very local Hong Kong restaurant. Typical Hong Kong business style. Focuses on efficiency but not so much on the looks of restaurant and food. Egg waffle has a crispy shell outside and a soft filling inside. The service was efficient - the waffle came after around 2 minutes of placing the order, but its freshly made.

The location was super convenient if you are coming by mtr though.

reviews.text: 地方污糟， 餐唔好味，價錢又唔平，冷氣又唔夠， 不會再去食👎
懷舊的環境，懷舊的食品，想找到青春的感覺路過記得進去試試，味道還不錯。
一代深水埗老店，轉手後，平準一落千丈！
首次試常餐，另加格仔餅，兩者都錯！
普通地道茶餐廳，早餐30多元，午餐就40元左右啦！
